These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
House: futuristic, cape-cod, tower, cottage
City: colone, hamburg, nizza, boston
1. the cottage house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
2. the futuristic house is on the right of the cottage house##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left or far right##3
4. the tower house is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to nizza##2
6. the cottage house is the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| House   | cottage | futuristic     | tower | cape-cod |
| City     | colone     | nizza | boston  | hamburg      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
City: berlin, rome, london, marseilles
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, cabbage, tomato, pineapple
1. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
2. the person eating pineapple is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
5. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| City   | berlin | rome    | marseilles     | london  |
| Food     | grapefruit    | tomato | cabbage | pineapple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, dancing, video-games, sudoku
4 different games are played: domino, canasta, monopoly, chess
1. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Hobby   | dancing   | video-games   | writing  | sudoku |
| Game           | canasta | chess | monopoly | domino  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, june, august, december
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, fanta, 7up, water
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person drinking 7up##2
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday         | june | september | december | august  |
| Beverage   | fanta  | lemonade   | water  | 7up |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, folk, rock, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indian, british, malaysian
1. the indian is on the far left##1
2. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of folk##1
3. the dutch is on the left or right of the indian##3
4. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of punk##1
5. the malaysian is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | folk   | rock | techno    |
| Nationality      | indian | dutch | british       | malaysian |

