.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
4 different games are played: chess, go, snooker, bridge
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, april, january, september
1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person playing snooker##2
3. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person playing chess##2
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
5. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Game    | chess | snooker | bridge | go |
| Birthday   | april | may  | january    | september  |

