.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, july, november
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, drawing, filmmaking, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in november##2
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's birthday is in november##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | june | november | july | february     |
| Hobby     | puzzles | rock-climbing  | drawing   | filmmaking |

