3. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person eating asparagus##1
4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
5. the person eating plum is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating peach is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
