.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, thriller, martial-arts, spy
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, june, december, october
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in june##2
3. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | thriller | martial-arts      | spy   |
| Birthday   | december  | june    | september | october |

