.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, june, april, january
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Birthday       | august | april | january    | june      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate       | soy-milk       | iced-tea | water |

