.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, juice
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, trike, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Beverage   | water     | soy-milk  | juice | hot-chocolate |
| Transport     | helicopter | motorbike | trike     | car    |

