.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, whist, scrabble
There 4 different types of food: mango, corn, peas, apricot
1. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3
4. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
5. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
6. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Game   | mah-jongg | whist  | scrabble | canasta |
| Food           | peas     | apricot | mango    | corn     |

