.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, garlic, raspberry, cucumber
House: gothic-revival, futuristic, tower, modern
1. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1
2. the futuristic house is on the left of the tower house##1
3. the person eating garlic is the modern house##1
4. the futuristic house is the person eating raspberry##1
5. the tower house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
6. the tower house is the person eating lemon##1
7. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Food         | garlic | cucumber | raspberry | lemon |
| House   | modern     | gothic-revival       | futuristic   | tower      |

