.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, fanta, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, dancing, magic-tricks, singing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | water | fanta | coffee |
| Hobby         | dancing  | magic-tricks   | singing | traveling     |

