.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, frog, rat, cat
City: edinburgh, san-francisco, new-york, prague
1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Pet      | snake | frog    | cat  | rat |
| City   | edinburgh       | san-francisco | new-york | prague  |

