3. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
4. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person playing billiard and the person driving the bus##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Game   | poker | snooker  | canasta  | billiard |
| Transport           | van    | bus | jet-ski | scooter |

