.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, time-travel
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, poppy, dahlia, bellflower
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
4. the person who growsorchid is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
6. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
7. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster     | crime     | horror          | time-travel |
| Flower      | orchid | poppy | bellflower | dahlia  |

 